flocking algorithm
===================

how to run:
------------

this script is writen in python. install python and Tinker
use command ,

	python display.py 

to run the script. you cann change the pattens of the birds by 
changing the  cohesion_rate, alignment_rate and separation_rate
in the display.py and SEPARATION_RADIOUS and COHESION_RADIOUS 
in flock.py.

